# Typography Audit & Harmonization Plan

## Context

The app's typography has grown organically across M3U, Stalker, and Xtream modules, resulting in inconsistent font sizes, weights, letter-spacing, and heading treatment. The goal is to harmonize typography to feel like a cohesive, modern, professional IPTV/streaming app (think Plex, Jellyfin, Apple TV).

## Visual Audit Summary (from screenshots)

- **Dashboard**: Clean — widget eyebrow/title hierarchy works well
- **Sources**: Good — `1.2rem/600` title with `0.875rem` subtitle
- **M3U Live TV / All Channels**: Category sidebar is clean, channel list items are good
- **Stalker Movies grid**: Good layout, card titles consistent
- **Stalker Movie detail**: Title is clean via `<app-content-hero>`
- **Stalker Live TV channels**: Channel items look good, EPG subtitle is readable
- **Xtream Movies/Live TV**: Matches Stalker well (shared components)
- **Recently Added**: `h2` and `h3` use browser defaults — **visually too large/bold**
- **Recently Viewed**: Page title styled but section titles inconsistent
- **Search**: Page `h2` inherits browser default — **oversized "Search" title**; empty state `h3` at `1.5rem` is too large
- **Favorites**: Page `h2` inherits browser default — **oversized**
- **Favorites layout no-items**: `p` at `1.1rem` — slightly large for empty state

## Typography Scale (Target)

| Role | Size | Weight | Letter-spacing | Usage |
|------|------|--------|----------------|-------|
| Page title | 1.2rem | 650 | -0.02em | h2 at top of full-page views |
| Section title | 1rem | 600 | -0.01em | h3 subsections, widget titles |
| Sidebar header | 0.94rem | 600 | -0.01em | Sidebar category title (no change) |
| Eyebrow | 0.72rem | 600 | 0.08em | Uppercase labels (no change) |
| Body | 0.875rem | 500 | 0 | Nav items, body text (no change) |
| Body small | 0.8rem | 500 | 0 | Metadata, counts |
| Empty state title | 1.05rem | 520 | -0.01em | All empty/no-results headings |
| Empty state hint | 0.85rem | 400 | 0 | Hint text below empty title |
| Card title | 0.8rem | 500 | 0 | Thumbnail card titles (no change) |
| Card meta | 0.7rem | 400 | 0 | Card dates (no change) |

## Implementation Steps

### Step 1: Fix Recently Added page — unstyled h2/h3

**File**: `libs/portal/xtream/feature/src/lib/recently-added/recently-added.component.scss`

Current `h2` rule (line 11-13): only `margin-bottom: 24px` — inherits browser default (~1.5em bold)
Current `h3` (lines 25-31): has `opacity: 0.8` but no font-size/weight — inherits browser default (~1.17em bold)

Change:
```scss
h2 {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 650;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.section h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    // keep existing display:flex, gap, margin-bottom, opacity
}
```

### Step 2: Fix Search layout — unstyled h2, oversized empty state

**File**: `libs/portal/shared/ui/src/lib/components/search-layout/search-layout.component.scss`

Current `.header-left h2` (line 53-56): only `margin: 0; white-space: nowrap;`
Current `.no-items-content h3` (line 117-121): `1.5rem / 500` — too large
Current `.no-items-content p` (line 124-128): `1.1rem` — slightly large

Change:
```scss
.header-left h2 {
    margin: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 650;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.no-items-content h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 520;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}

.no-items-content p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.65;
}
```

### Step 3: Fix Recently Viewed section titles

**File**: `libs/portal/xtream/feature/src/lib/recently-viewed/recently-viewed.component.scss`

Current `.playlist-title` (h3): `1.1rem / 500` — slightly large and light weight

Change:
```scss
.playlist-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    // keep other properties
}
```

### Step 4: Fix Search Results section/playlist titles

**File**: `libs/portal/xtream/feature/src/lib/search-results/search-results.component.scss`

Current `.section-title`: `1.2rem / normal` with secondary color — inconsistent style
Current `.playlist-title`: `1.1rem / 500`

Change:
```scss
.section-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--mat-sys-on-surface);
}

.playlist-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
}
```

### Step 5: Fix Xtream Account Info h3

**File**: `libs/portal/xtream/feature/src/lib/account-info/account-info.component.scss`

Current `.info-section h3`: `1.1em` with no weight specified

Change:
```scss
.info-section h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
```

### Step 6: Fix Favorites Layout no-items

**File**: `libs/portal/shared/ui/src/lib/components/favorites-layout/favorites-layout.component.scss`

Current `.no-items p` (line 105-108): `1.1rem` — too large for empty state

Change:
```scss
.no-items p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0.65;
}
```

### Step 7: Harmonize M3U channel list empty states

**Files**:
- `libs/ui/components/src/lib/channel-list-container/all-channels-view/all-channels-view.component.scss`
  - `.no-results-title`: 1.1rem/500 -> 1.05rem/520/-0.01em
  - `.no-results-hint`: 0.9rem -> 0.85rem, opacity 0.7 -> 0.65

- `libs/ui/components/src/lib/channel-list-container/favorites-view/favorites-view.component.scss`
  - `.empty-favorites` (uses `<strong>`): add font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 520
  - `.empty-favorites-hint`: 0.9rem -> 0.85rem, opacity 0.7 -> 0.65

- `libs/ui/components/src/lib/channel-list-container/recent-view/recent-view.component.scss`
  - Same pattern as favorites-view

### Step 8: Fix Portal empty state

**File**: `libs/portal/shared/ui/src/lib/components/portal-empty-state/portal-empty-state.component.scss`

Current `.empty-state-title`: `1.1rem / 500 / -0.01em / opacity: 0.5`

Change:
```scss
.empty-state-title {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 520;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    opacity: 0.5;
}
```
(Minor tweak — just size and weight alignment)

### Step 9: Fix Global Favorites empty state (px -> rem)

**File**: `libs/workspace/shell/feature/src/lib/global-favorites/global-favorites-list.component.scss`

Current `.empty-title`: `14px / 500` and `.empty-hint`: `12px / 0.7 opacity`

Change:
```scss
.empty-title {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 520;
