.empty-hint {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0.65;
}
```

### Step 10: Fix Stalker detail section titles (oversized)

**File**: `libs/portal/stalker/feature/src/lib/styles/detail-view.scss`

Current `.content-section__title`: `1.375rem / 600` — too large for a subsection
Current `.youtube-trailer h3`: `1.125rem / 600` — slightly oversized

