### Step 11: Fix channel-list-item letter-spacing

**File**: `libs/ui/components/src/lib/channel-list-container/channel-list-item/channel-list-item.component.scss`

Current `.channel-name`: `letter-spacing: 0.01em` (loosens text)

Change to: `letter-spacing: -0.01em` (tighter, matches professional headings)

